Many of those who work on tan (gold medicine) are ignorant of the method of
fixing shên (appearance). This does not depend upon swiftness or slowness.
The fixing consists in condensing sAên into the interior of the essence
(ching). Fixing shên, in other words, is extinguishing all desires and
returning shên to the mind. When this is done, one may see the whole figure
of hsing (character, nature).
